# Agent 5.0 Official Architecture Whitepaper
Version 1.0 | June 2026
Target Audience: FUTO Foundation, NLnet Foundation, Sentient Foundation, Open Source AI Researchers, GitHub Contributors, Research Investors

## Preface
This document serves as the authoritative architectural reference for Agent 5.0, an open-source autonomous cognitive operating system. It excludes product marketing language, exaggerated claims, and unsubstantiated performance descriptions. All content strictly adheres to the finalized core architecture scope of Agent 5.0; no new runtime modules, functional extensions or experimental logic are added.

Distinction markers used throughout:
- ✅ Implemented: Fully integrated into main branch
- 🟡 In Progress: Active development, partial core logic validated
- 🔵 Research Direction: Long-term planned architecture, not yet engineered

